description:
Application to drive DCC-EX command station via Bluetooth
Rich set of features to control model railroad layout:
- Locomotives library and control panel (cab);
- Accessories library with control from the list;
- Routes (groups of accessories with states);
- Read/write CVs and CV bits.

ESU LokPilot 5 decoder helper: outputs config and mapping.

Finger-friendly navigation, swipe between lists and locomotives in cab.
